      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "This workflow restores faded colour photographs. It does not colourize black-and-white photographs.\n\nThe default path is non-generative: it changes only colour and tone, never facial structure or composition.\n\nFor local repair, paint WHITE only on the damaged area in the Load Image Mask Editor. The crop tools below are deliberately disconnected until you choose to use them."
      ]
    },
