      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Enable AI Colour Repair is intentionally not on the default path. Use it only for a masked area whose colour information is genuinely absent.\n\nNever mask an entire recognizable face. Mask only damaged pixels. Reconstruction cannot recover exact details that no longer exist."
      ]
